description: Chef Seb Gourmet Truck is founded by Chef Sebastian Oveysi and Marcia Stone. It’s an extension of Amoo’s kitchen in Mclean VA. This gourmet truck will feature 3 of Amoo’s signature and award winning dishes such as the Chilean sea bass, the chicken breast filet, and the lamb tenderloin filet kabobs along with specialties that will change every day. The goal is to serve some of the healthiest organic cuisine that is influenced by different regions of the world and transformed into culinary masterpieces by Chef Seb.
name: Chef Seb on Wheels
